01:18:51.970 --> 01:18:54.870
the Dk is greater than
1, because if it's

01:18:54.870 --> 01:18:58.740
one dimensional, it's
just one basis vector one

01:18:58.740 --> 01:19:01.250
eigenvector, end of the story.

01:19:01.250 --> 01:19:04.250
Now this thing, by
