01:19:10.010 --> 01:19:11.810
to find an orthonormal basis.

01:19:11.810 --> 01:19:17.080
The theorem guarantees it,
so these are all orthonormal.

01:19:17.080 --> 01:19:20.300
So at the end of the day,
