01:19:20.300 --> 01:19:28.470
of the vector space, V as U1
plus U2 plus maybe up to UM.

01:19:31.660 --> 01:19:36.330
And all of these vector
spaces like U's here, they

01:19:36.330 --> 01:19:39.340
