01:27:09.490 --> 01:27:12.320
And you can have a matrix here.

01:27:12.320 --> 01:27:17.720
And if you act on the second
Uk U2, you get a vector in U2,

01:27:17.720 --> 01:27:20.150
so it's orthogonal to
